"nofollow ugc\">khc phc s c hu ch ca chng ti hng dn</a>.</p>\n<p>Nu bn nhn thy li sau khi cp nht giao din hoc plugin, c th c s c tng thch gia n v WooCommerce. Nu s c xut hin sau khi cp nht WooCommerce, c th c xung t gia WooCommerce v giao din hoc plugin li thi.</p>\n<p>Trong c hai trng hp, chng ti khuyn bn nn chy th nghim xung t bng cch s dng <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/troubleshooting-using-health-check/?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\"> Kim tra tnh trng</a> (cho php bn tt ch  v plugin m khng nh hng n khch truy cp) hoc khc phc s c bng cch s dng <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/document/how-to-test-for-conflicts/#section-3?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">trang web t chc</a>.</p>\n</p>\n<dt id=\'where%20can%20i%20report%20bugs%3F\'>\nTi c th bo co li  u?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Bo co li trn <a href=\"https://github.com/woocommerce/woocommerce/issues?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">kho lu tr WooCommerce GitHub</a>. Bn cng c th thng bo cho chng ti qua din n h tr ca chng ti  hy nh tm kim trn din n  xc nhn rng li cha c bo co.</p>\n</p>\n<dt id=\'where%20can%20i%20request%20new%20features%2C%20themes%2C%20and%20extensions%3F\'>\nTi c th yu cu cc tnh nng, giao din v tin ch m rng mi  u?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yu cu cc tnh nng v tin ch m rng mi cng nh b phiu cho cc  xut hin c trn <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/feature-requests/woocommerce?utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=wordpress.org&amp;utm_campaign=wp_org_repo_listing\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">bng yu cu tnh nng chnh thc ca chng ti </a>. Nhm Sn phm ca chng ti thng xuyn xem xt cc yu cu v coi chng c gi tr cho vic lp k hoch sn phm.</p>\n</p>\n<dt id=\'woocommerce%20is%20awesome%21%20can%20i%20contribute%3F\'>\nWooCommerce tht tuyt vi! Ti c th tham gia ng gp khng?\n</h4>\n<p>\n<p>Vng, bn c th! Hy t