trong>thng c xy dng ti ni c sui khong t nhin, bao quanh l ni non, rng xanh hay thm ch c tuyt trng vo ma ng.\r\n\r\nVi du khch, tri nghim onsen ln u l dp c bit  chm vo mt kha cnh i sng rt tht, rt i ca ngi Nht, th m bn khng th thy ch bng vic do quanh<a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-tokyo.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">Tokyo</a>hay<a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-osaka.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">Osaka</a>.  l ni bn bung b thit b cng ngh, ngi xung v ht th tht su trong ln hi nc m.\r\n<h4><strong>Lu  quan trng trc khi n onsen Nht Bn</strong></h4>\r\n<strong><a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-nhat-ban.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">Vn ha onsen Nht Bn</a></strong>c nhng quy nh kh nghim ngt v i khi gy bi ri cho ngi ln u. Nhng hiu r t trc s gip bn t tin v tn hng trn vn tri nghim ny.\r\n\r\nVn  u tin l hnh xm. Nhiu onsen truyn thng khng chp nhn khch c hnh xm do lin quan n hnh nh yakuza trong vn ha Nht. Tuy nhin, nhng nm gn y, ngy cng nhiu khu onsen m hn vi du khch nc ngoi. Bn c th tm nhng ni ghi r \"tattoo-friendly\" hoc thu onsen ring nu mun thoi mi hn.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://media.vietravel.com/images/Content/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"470\" height=\"314\" />\r\n\r\nV  tm, ng mang theo o tm vo bn nc. Cch tm sui nc nng Nht l tm kha thn hon ton. Tuy iu ny c th khin bn lng tng, nhng s tht l khng ai   n bn. Mi ngi u gi khong cch v tn trng khng gian ring.\r\n\r\nMt s vt dng nn mang theo gm khn nh ( lau mt), khn ln (lau ngi sau khi tm), kp tc nu bn c tc di, v  skincare  dng sau khi tm. Nhiu onsen  trang b y  nhng bn vn nn chun b trc  an tm.\r\n<h4><strong>Hng dn cch tm sui nc nng Nht ng chun</strong></h4>\r\nB quyt  tn hng onsen Nht Bn ng cch bt u t vic... khng vi. ng nhy o xung bn nc ngay khi n ni. Hy bt u bng vic v sinh tht k. Mi khu onsen u c khu tm trng ring vi vi sen thp, gh nha nh v cc sn phm tm. Ngi xung, dng vi sen ra sch ton thn, gi u nu cn v m bo khng cn m hi hay bi bn trc khi bc vo bn.\r\n\r\nKhi  sch s, bn bc nh nhng vo bn nc m. Khn nh khng c mang vo nc, bn c th  trn u hoc  trn thnh bn. Nc thng rt nng, khong 4042  C, nn hy t t ngm chn trc ri mi h ngi dn dn.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://media.vietravel.com/images/Content/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"494\" height=\"371\" />\r\n\r\nTrong bn, hn ch ni chuyn ln ting. Cch tm sui nc nng Nht ch trng s yn tnh. y l lc  bn lng nghe ting nc, cm nhn hi nng len li vo c bp mt mi v  u c hon ton c ngh ngi.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://media.vietravel.com/images/Content/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"562\" height=\"375\" />\r\n<h4><strong>Tri nghim onsen ln u  Cm gic ra sao?</strong></h4>\r\nBan u, cm gic ngi l iu khng th trnh khi.<strong><a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-nhat-ban.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">Tri nghim onsen</a></strong>ln u thng l c sc nh vi nhng ai khng quen kha thn ni cng cng. Nhng ch sau vi pht, bn s thy ai cng nh ai  ngi Nht c cch rt vn minh trong vic gi khong cch v khng nh gi ngi khc. Khi vt qua c ro cn tm l , bn s hiu v sao ngi ta li m onsen n vy.\r\n\r\nC th bn nh c phc hi: cn au lng du li, gic ng m  su hn, ln da sau khi ngm nc khong tr nn mm mi l thng. Nhng khng ch c vy, onsen cn gip tm tr bn c \"reset\" mi lo toan tm thi tan bin gia hi nc m o.\r\n\r\nSau khi tm sui nc nng Nht Bn, ng vi ri i. Nhiu ngi Nht s ngh ngi trong phng ch, nhm nhi chai sa ti lnh  y mt \"nghi l\" nh khng th thiu sau mi ln i onsen Nht Bn. Cm gic khi y l s hi lng, nh nhm v mt cht... nghin.\r\n<h4><strong>Gi  khu onsen l tng cho ngi ln u tri nghim</strong></h4>\r\nNu bn cha tng th tri nghim onsen ln u, nn chn nhng ni va p, va thn thin vi ngi nc ngoi. Gi  u tin l Hakone  mt vng ni gn Tokyo, ni ting vi onsen l thin nhn ra<strong><a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-nui-phu-si.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">ni Ph S</a></strong>.  y, dch v a dng, bin ch dn r rng, rt d tip cn.\r\n\r\nTip theo l Beppu  thnh ph onsen ln nht Nht Bn. Ngoi hng chc nh tm nc nng, Beppu cn c \"a ngc onsen\"  ni nc sui si sc mu xanh,  nh trong truyn thn thoi.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone\" style=\"margin: 8px 8px 0px;\" src=\"https://media.vietravel.com/images/Content/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-5135.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"413\" height=\"275\" />\r\n\r\nCui cng, nu bn thch v c knh th Kinosaki l la chn l tng. Lng nh xinh ny c by nh tm cng cng, khch thng mc yukata i b t onsen ny sang onsen khc, y mt tri nghim rt nn th nu bn mun sng nh ngi Nht tht s.\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-nhat-ban.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">Onsen Nht Bn</a></strong>khng ch l ni  ngm mnh, m cn l cnh ca dn bn vo mt phn vn ha su sc ca x s hoa anh o. Mi ln tm l mt ln bung b mt mi, np li nng lng v lng nghe chnh c th mnh. D bn c lo lng hay e d tri nghim onsen ln u, hy th. V ch khi dm bc vo ln nc nng y, bn mi thc s hiu c s tinh t trong cch tm sui nc nng Nht, mt ngh thut chm sc bn thn t tn gc r.','Onsen Nht Bn  Nhiu hn mt ni  tm','','publish','open','open','','onsen-nhat-ban-nhieu-hon-mot-noi-de-tam','','','2025-11-24 02:03:23','2025-11-24 02:03:23','',0,'http://localhost:8080/?p=180',0,'post','',0),(181,1,'2025-11-24 01:14:47','2025-11-24 01:14:47','','huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-4','','inherit','open','closed','','huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-4','','','2025-11-24 01:14:47','2025-11-24 01:14:47','',180,'http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-4.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(182,1,'2025-11-24 01:17:43','2025-11-24 01:17:43','<h2><em>Ln u tri nghim onsen Nht Bn ln u 