ng nn mang theo gm khn nh ( lau mt), khn ln (lau ngi sau khi tm), kp tc nu bn c tc di, v  skincare  dng sau khi tm. Nhiu onsen  trang b y  nhng bn vn nn chun b trc  an tm.\r\n<h2><strong>Hng dn cch tm sui nc nng Nht ng chun</strong></h2>\r\nB quyt  tn hng onsen Nht Bn ng cch bt u t vic... khng vi. ng nhy o xung bn nc ngay khi n ni. Hy bt u bng vic v sinh tht k. Mi khu onsen u c khu tm trng ring vi vi sen thp, gh nha nh v cc sn phm tm. Ngi xung, dng vi sen ra sch ton thn, gi u nu cn v m bo khng cn m hi hay bi bn trc khi bc vo bn.\r\n\r\nKhi  sch s, bn bc nh nhng vo bn nc m. Khn nh\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://media.vietravel.com/images/Content/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1336\" />\r\n\r\nkhng c mang vo nc, bn c th  trn u hoc  trn thnh bn. Nc thng rt nng, khong 4042  C, nn hy t t ngm chn trc ri mi h ngi dn dn.\r\n\r\nTrong bn, hn ch ni chuyn ln ting. Cch tm sui nc nng Nht ch trng s yn tnh. y l lc  bn lng nghe ting nc, cm nhn hi nng len li vo c bp mt mi v  u c hon ton c ngh ngi.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https://media.vietravel.com/images/Content/huong-dan-tam-onsen-suoi-nuoc-nong-dung-kieu-nhat-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1295\" />\r\n<h2><strong>Tri nghim onsen ln u  Cm gic ra sao?</strong></h2>\r\nBan u, cm gic ngi l iu khng th trnh khi.<strong><a href=\"https://travel.com.vn/du-lich-nhat-ban.aspx?utm_source=DIGI_Google&amp;utm_medium=SEOPost&amp;utm_campaign=SEOPost\">Tri nghim onsen</a></strong>ln u thng l c sc nh vi nhng ai khng quen kha thn ni cng cng. Nhng ch sau vi pht, bn s thy ai cng nh ai  ngi Nht c cch rt vn minh trong vic gi khong cch v khng nh gi ngi khc. Khi vt qua c ro cn tm l , bn s hiu v sao ngi ta li m onsen n vy.\r\n\r\nC th bn nh c phc hi: cn au lng du li, gic ng m  su hn, ln da sau khi ngm nc khong tr nn mm mi l thng. Nhng khng ch c vy, onsen cn gip tm tr bn c \"reset\" mi lo toan tm thi tan bin gia hi nc m o.\r\n\r\nSau khi tm sui nc nng Nht Bn, ng vi ri i. Nhiu ngi Nht